    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
        <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
            <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl" role="heading">
                Find postgraduate teacher training in business studies
            </h1>
            <p class="govuk-body-l">
                Use this service to search and compare postgraduate teacher training courses in England.
            </p>

            <a href='@Url.Action("Disclaimer", "Home")' class="govuk-button govuk-button--start" role="button">Start now</a>

            <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">
                What you’ll need
            </h2>

            <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">GCSEs</h3>

            <p class="govuk-body">To apply for a course you’ll need grade 4 (previously grade C) GCSEs in maths and English.</p>

            <p class="govuk-body">If you want to teach in a primary school you’ll also need a minimum grade 4 in a science subject.</p>

            <p class="govuk-body">If you don’t have these qualifications, you must prove you have the equivalent level of knowledge in these subjects.</p>

            <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Degree</h3>

            <p class="govuk-body">You’ll need a UK degree, or the international equivalent.</p>

            <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Tests and checks</h3>

            <p class="govuk-body">Before you start the course you’ll need to:</p>

            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                <li>pass literacy and numeracy skills tests</li>
                <li>have a Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) security check</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">
                If you don&#8217;t want to teach business&nbsp;studies
            </h2>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                You can
                <a href="https://www.ucas.com/ucas/teacher-training/ucas-teacher-training-search-training-programmes" class="govuk-link">find all teacher training courses</a>
                on the UCAS website.
            </p>

            <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">
                Other ways into teaching
            </h2>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                Find out more about teaching:
            </p>
            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                <li>
                if you <a href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/explore-my-options/teacher-training-routes/university-led-training/university-led-undergraduate-training">don’t have a degree</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                if you <a href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/explore-my-options/teacher-training-routes/specialist-training-options/assessment-only">have a degree and teaching experience already</a>&nbsp;–&nbsp;you might not need to do any more training
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://www.teachfirst.org.uk/" class="govuk-link">young people from poorer backgrounds</a>, through Teach First
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
